Text: How do you install?  Like, from which of the three zip files?
with of the zip files do i extract there are 3

For those having difficulty reading files names:

VSE stands for VirusScan Enterprise - install this first, but only after you've uninstalled any other anti-virus software!
MDF is the firewall,
and by process of elimination, we can work out that MAntispywareModule means that's the Antispyware.
